Michael Easy, 29, from Southampton, sparked a nationwide police manhunt after going on the run in 2013 after attacking a woman at a party .
He posted pictures of himself on Facebook posing in a platinum wig and Dame Edna Everage-style glasses under the profile name of Michelle Dirt .
But officers eventually found him and he was jailed for 15 months for breaching a restraining order and assaulting two prison guards while at Winchester Prison .